ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectKuwait - Agreement on the Promotion and the Protection of Investments ** RATIFICATION **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT FOR THE PROMOTION AND THE PROTECTION OF INVESTMENTS between Canada and the STATE OF KUWAIT.
